sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant System as System
    participant Widget as Widget

    User->>System: Request Home-Screen Widgets
    System->>Widget: Fetch available widgets
    Widget-->>System: Return widget list
    System-->>User: Display available widgets
    User->>Widget: Select a widget
    Widget-->>User: Show widget details
    User->>System: Add widget to home screen
    System-->>User: Confirm widget addition